---
title: Korean Eggplant & Baby Broccoli Stir-Fry  with Garlic Rice & Mayonnaise
description: Eggplant is known in our storybooks as the veggie ruler! Dress it in the finest sweet and soy flavours and roast it in the oven for a depth of
flavour you didn’t know was possible. Served with garlicky rice and stir-fried veggies, this warming dish is sure to be a crowd pleaser.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
